article_html: An intruder evaded security and jumped off the high board into the pool during the men’s 10m final during the Fina/NVC Diving World Series at the Aquatics Centre in London, before subsequently being carted away. The incident was captured on video by one member of the audience, which shows the crowd booing the man after his leap. Tom Daley later won gold in the men’s 10m platform event, while Canada’s Roseline Filion won the women’s event
